name: OSS con Numeros
query:
SELECT `Regnumber`,
    `customer_name`,
    `company`,
    `departamento`,
    `municipio`,
    `portafolio`,
    `estado_cliente`,
    `tipo_de_cliente`,
    `barrio`,
    `direccion`,
    `saldo`,
    c.phone,
    `0_30`,
    `30_60`,
    `60_90`,
    `90_120`,
    `120_150`,
    `150_180`,
    `180_210`,
    `210_240`,
    `240_270`,
    `270_300`,
    `300_330`,
    `330_360`,
    `360_390`,
    `390_420`,
    `420_450`,
    `450_480`,
    `480_510`,
    `510_540`,
    `540_570`,
    `570_600`,
    `600_630`,
    `630_660`,
    `660_690`,
    `690_720`,
    `720_MAS`
from vw_saldos720_mas_portafolio_colector as s left outer join `tabDynamic Link` as dl on s.Regnumber=dl.link_name inner join 
`tabContact Phone` as c on dl.link_title=c.parent limit 50000;
